{
  "stem": "12684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, they could just take the jewelry and a few things out of the house or their apartments.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so it was a constant goodbye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were emigrating to the States or wherever, whoever was the quota the largest where they could get into, in which country.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I believe that my grandfather had plans, but all this went away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only know that Grandfather had made plans, but something very unfortunate happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother's brother-in-law fled the country, and as punishment for that, we could not cross the borders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he left illegally and then my grandfather was thrown into prison and came out again, but he could never leave the country under any circumstances.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Germans realized that my uncle had fled the country and diverted some money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I wasn't allowed to visit him in prison.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't want that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was able to see him and his wife was able to see him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, when he came back, he looked very shopworn, to say the least, and was very tired.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't speak much about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] aghast about what had happened to him on account of his son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it worked very hard on his mind, particularly that he realized that we could not leave the country and whatever was coming was coming and we could not get away.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was not allowed to write, not to use the telephone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just could have, you know, his wife or my mother come to see him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was in the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in Hamburg, in the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could take you there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
